{"key":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01|Php|1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","chapter":1,"textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024","parserRevision":"v10","verses":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":1,"verse":1,"text":"Paul and Timothy, servants of Christ Jesus:","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":1,"verse":2,"text":"Grace to you and peace from God our Father and the Lord Jesus Christ.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":1,"verse":3,"text":"I give thanks to my God for every remembrance of you,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:4","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":1,"verse":4,"text":"always praying with joy for all of you in my every prayer,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:5","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":1,"verse":5,"text":"because of your partnership in the gospel from the first day until now.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:6","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":1,"verse":6,"text":"I am sure of this, that he who started a good work in you will carry it on to completion until the day of Christ Jesus.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:7","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":1,"verse":7,"text":"Indeed, it is right for me to think this way about all of you, because I have you in my heart, and you are all partners with me in grace, both in my imprisonment and in the defense and confirmation of the gospel.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:8","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":1,"verse":8,"text":"For God is my witness, how deeply I miss all of you with the affection of Christ Jesus.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:9","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":1,"verse":9,"text":"And I pray this: that your love will keep on growing in knowledge and every kind of discernment,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:10","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":1,"verse":10,"text":"so that you may approve the things that are superior and may be pure and blameless in the day of Christ,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:11","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":1,"verse":11,"text":"filled with the fruit of righteousness that comes through Jesus Christ to the glory and praise of God.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:12","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":1,"verse":12,"text":"Now I want you to know, brothers and sisters, that what has happened to me has actually advanced the gospel, Ac 21–26","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:13","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":1,"verse":13,"text":"so that it has become known throughout the whole imperial guard, and to everyone else, that my imprisonment is because I am in Christ.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:14","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":1,"verse":14,"text":"Most of the brothers have gained confidence in the Lord from my imprisonment and dare even more to speak the word fearlessly.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:15","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":1,"verse":15,"text":"To be sure, some preach Christ out of envy and rivalry, but others out of good will.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:16","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":1,"verse":16,"text":"These preach out of love, knowing that I am appointed for the defense of the gospel;","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:17","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":1,"verse":17,"text":"the others proclaim Christ out of selfish ambition, not sincerely, thinking that they will cause me trouble in my imprisonment.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:18","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":1,"verse":18,"text":"What does it matter? Only that in every way, whether from false motives or true, Christ is proclaimed, and in this I rejoice. Yes, and I will continue to rejoice","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:19","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":1,"verse":19,"text":"because I know this will lead to my salvation through your prayers and help from the Spirit of Jesus Christ.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:20","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":1,"verse":20,"text":"My eager expectation and hope is that I will not be ashamed about anything, but that now as always, with all courage, Christ will be highly honored in my body, whether by life or by death.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:21","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":1,"verse":21,"text":"For me, to live is Christ and to die is gain.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:22","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":1,"verse":22,"text":"Now if I live on in the flesh, this means fruitful work for me; and I don’t know which one I should choose.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:23","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":1,"verse":23,"text":"I am torn between the two. I long to depart and be with Christ —which is far better —","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:24","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":1,"verse":24,"text":"but to remain in the flesh is more necessary for your sake.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:25","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":1,"verse":25,"text":"Since I am persuaded of this, I know that I will remain and continue with all of you for your progress and joy in the faith,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:26","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":1,"verse":26,"text":"so that, because of my coming to you again, your boasting in Christ Jesus may abound.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:27","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":1,"verse":27,"text":"Just one thing: As citizens of heaven, live your life worthy of the gospel of Christ. Then, whether I come and see you or am absent, I will hear about you that you are standing firm in one spirit, in one accord, contending together for the faith of the gospel,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:28","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":1,"verse":28,"text":"not being frightened in any way by your opponents. This is a sign of destruction for them, but of your salvation —and this is from God.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:29","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":1,"verse":29,"text":"For it has been granted to you on Christ’s behalf not only to believe in him, but also to suffer for him,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:30","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","bookOrder":49,"chapter":1,"verse":30,"text":"since you are engaged in the same struggle that you saw I had and now hear that I have.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"}],"layout":{"bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Php","chapter":1,"paragraphStarts":[1,2,3,12,21,27],"headings":[{"beforeVerse":1,"text":"Greeting"},{"beforeVerse":3,"text":"Thanksgiving and Prayer"},{"beforeVerse":12,"text":"Advance of the Gospel"},{"beforeVerse":21,"text":"Living Is Christ"}],"poetryBlocks":[],"studyByVerse":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:1","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Paul "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 13:9","book":"Act","chapter":13,"verse":9,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" and Timothy, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 16:1","book":"Act","chapter":16,"verse":1,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Tm 1:2","book":"1Ti","chapter":1,"verse":2,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" servants of Christ Jesus:"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 13:9","book":"Act","chapter":13,"verse":9},{"label":"Ac 16:1","book":"Act","chapter":16,"verse":1},{"label":"1Tm 1:2","book":"1Ti","chapter":1,"verse":2}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:2","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Grace to you and peace from God our Father and the Lord Jesus Christ."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:3","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I give thanks to my God for every remembrance of you, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or for your every remembrance of me"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or for your every remembrance of me"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:4","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"always praying with joy for all of you in my every prayer, "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:5","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"because of your partnership in the gospel from the first day "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 16:12–40","book":"Act","chapter":16,"verse":12,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" until now. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 9:15–18","book":"1Co","chapter":9,"verse":15,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 11:7–9","book":"2Co","chapter":11,"verse":7,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 4:10","book":"Php","chapter":4,"verse":10,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 4:16","book":"Php","chapter":4,"verse":16,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 4:18","book":"Php","chapter":4,"verse":18,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 16:12–40","book":"Act","chapter":16,"verse":12},{"label":"1Co 9:15–18","book":"1Co","chapter":9,"verse":15},{"label":"2Co 11:7–9","book":"2Co","chapter":11,"verse":7},{"label":"Php 4:10","book":"Php","chapter":4,"verse":10},{"label":"Php 4:16","book":"Php","chapter":4,"verse":16},{"label":"Php 4:18","book":"Php","chapter":4,"verse":18}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:6","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I am sure of this, that he who started a good work "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 9:8","book":"2Co","chapter":9,"verse":8,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 3:10","book":"Gal","chapter":3,"verse":10,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" in you "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Or work among you"},{"kind":"text","text":" will carry it on to completion "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 7:1","book":"2Co","chapter":7,"verse":1,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" until the day of Christ Jesus. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Co 9:8","book":"2Co","chapter":9,"verse":8},{"label":"Gl 3:10","book":"Gal","chapter":3,"verse":10},{"label":"2Co 7:1","book":"2Co","chapter":7,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"Or work among you"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:7","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Indeed, it is right "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 1:17","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":17,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" for me to think this way about all of you, because I have you in my heart, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":3,"text":"Or because you have me in your heart"},{"kind":"text","text":" and you are all partners with me in grace, both in my imprisonment "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 1:13–14","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":13,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 1:17","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":17,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 1:25","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":25,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 2:17","book":"Php","chapter":2,"verse":17,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 2:24","book":"Php","chapter":2,"verse":24,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 4:22","book":"Php","chapter":4,"verse":22,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" and in the defense "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 22:1","book":"Act","chapter":22,"verse":1,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"text","text":" and confirmation of the gospel. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 1:17","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":17},{"label":"Php 1:13–14","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":13},{"label":"Php 1:17","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":17},{"label":"Php 1:25","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":25},{"label":"Php 2:17","book":"Php","chapter":2,"verse":17},{"label":"Php 2:24","book":"Php","chapter":2,"verse":24},{"label":"Php 4:22","book":"Php","chapter":4,"verse":22},{"label":"Ac 22:1","book":"Act","chapter":22,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[{"marker":3,"text":"Or because you have me in your heart"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:8","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For God is my witness, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 1:9","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":9,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" how deeply I miss all of you "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Th 3:6","book":"1Th","chapter":3,"verse":6,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" with the affection of Christ Jesus. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 1:9","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":9},{"label":"1Th 3:6","book":"1Th","chapter":3,"verse":6}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:9","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"And I pray this: that your love "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 13:1","book":"1Co","chapter":13,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" will keep on growing "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 15:58","book":"1Co","chapter":15,"verse":58,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" in knowledge and every kind of discernment, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 5:17","book":"Eph","chapter":5,"verse":17,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Co 13:1","book":"1Co","chapter":13,"verse":1},{"label":"1Co 15:58","book":"1Co","chapter":15,"verse":58},{"label":"Eph 5:17","book":"Eph","chapter":5,"verse":17}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"so that you may approve the things that are superior "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 12:2","book":"Rom","chapter":12,"verse":2,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" and may be pure "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Pt 3:1","book":"2Pe","chapter":3,"verse":1,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" and blameless "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 24:16","book":"Act","chapter":24,"verse":16,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 10:32","book":"1Co","chapter":10,"verse":32,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" in the day of Christ, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 1:6","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":6,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 1:15","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":15,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 12:2","book":"Rom","chapter":12,"verse":2},{"label":"2Pt 3:1","book":"2Pe","chapter":3,"verse":1},{"label":"Ac 24:16","book":"Act","chapter":24,"verse":16},{"label":"1Co 10:32","book":"1Co","chapter":10,"verse":32},{"label":"Php 1:6","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":6},{"label":"Php 1:15","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":15}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"filled with the fruit "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 3:8","book":"Mat","chapter":3,"verse":8,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 5:22","book":"Gal","chapter":5,"verse":22,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" of righteousness "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 1:17","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":17,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" that comes through Jesus Christ to the glory "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 9:32","book":"Luk","chapter":9,"verse":32,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 17:24","book":"Jhn","chapter":17,"verse":24,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 3:18","book":"2Co","chapter":3,"verse":18,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Pt 3:18","book":"2Pe","chapter":3,"verse":18,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" and praise of God."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 3:8","book":"Mat","chapter":3,"verse":8},{"label":"Gl 5:22","book":"Gal","chapter":5,"verse":22},{"label":"Rm 1:17","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":17},{"label":"Lk 9:32","book":"Luk","chapter":9,"verse":32},{"label":"Jn 17:24","book":"Jhn","chapter":17,"verse":24},{"label":"2Co 3:18","book":"2Co","chapter":3,"verse":18},{"label":"2Pt 3:18","book":"2Pe","chapter":3,"verse":18}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Now I want you to know, brothers and sisters, that what has happened to me has actually advanced the gospel, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 13:9","book":"Mrk","chapter":13,"verse":9,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":"Ac 21–26 "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mk 13:9","book":"Mrk","chapter":13,"verse":9}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"so that it has become known throughout the whole imperial guard, and to everyone else, that my imprisonment is because I am in Christ. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Most of the brothers have gained confidence in the Lord from my imprisonment and dare even more to speak the word "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss add of God"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 8:21","book":"Luk","chapter":8,"verse":21,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 18:32","book":"Jhn","chapter":18,"verse":32,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 17:11","book":"Act","chapter":17,"verse":11,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 4:12","book":"Heb","chapter":4,"verse":12,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" fearlessly. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lk 8:21","book":"Luk","chapter":8,"verse":21},{"label":"Jn 18:32","book":"Jhn","chapter":18,"verse":32},{"label":"Ac 17:11","book":"Act","chapter":17,"verse":11},{"label":"Heb 4:12","book":"Heb","chapter":4,"verse":12}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss add of God"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"To be sure, some preach Christ out of envy and rivalry, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 1:29","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":29,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ti 3:9","book":"Tit","chapter":3,"verse":9,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" but others out of good will. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 1:29","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":29},{"label":"Ti 3:9","book":"Tit","chapter":3,"verse":9}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"These preach out of love, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 13:1","book":"1Co","chapter":13,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" knowing that I am appointed for the defense of the gospel; "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Co 13:1","book":"1Co","chapter":13,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"the others proclaim Christ out of selfish ambition, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 2:8","book":"Rom","chapter":2,"verse":8,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" not sincerely, thinking that they will cause me trouble in my imprisonment. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 2:8","book":"Rom","chapter":2,"verse":8}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"What does it matter? Only that in every way, whether from false motives "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Th 2:5","book":"1Th","chapter":2,"verse":5,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" or true, Christ is proclaimed, and in this I rejoice. Yes, and I will continue to rejoice "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Th 2:5","book":"1Th","chapter":2,"verse":5}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"because I know this will lead to my salvation "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Or vindication"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jb 13:16","book":"Job","chapter":13,"verse":16,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" through your prayers and help from the Spirit "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 5:25","book":"Gal","chapter":5,"verse":25,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" of Jesus Christ. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 16:7","book":"Act","chapter":16,"verse":7,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 8:9","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":9,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 1:11","book":"1Pe","chapter":1,"verse":11,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jb 13:16","book":"Job","chapter":13,"verse":16},{"label":"Gl 5:25","book":"Gal","chapter":5,"verse":25},{"label":"Ac 16:7","book":"Act","chapter":16,"verse":7},{"label":"Rm 8:9","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":9},{"label":"1Pt 1:11","book":"1Pe","chapter":1,"verse":11}],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"Or vindication"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"My eager expectation and hope "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 23:6","book":"Act","chapter":23,"verse":6,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Th 1:3","book":"1Th","chapter":1,"verse":3,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" is that I will not be ashamed about anything, but that now as always, with all courage, Christ will be highly honored in my body, whether by life "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Jn 5:12","book":"1Jn","chapter":5,"verse":12,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" or by death. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 8:51","book":"Jhn","chapter":8,"verse":51,"letter":"d"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 23:6","book":"Act","chapter":23,"verse":6},{"label":"1Th 1:3","book":"1Th","chapter":1,"verse":3},{"label":"1Jn 5:12","book":"1Jn","chapter":5,"verse":12},{"label":"Jn 8:51","book":"Jhn","chapter":8,"verse":51}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:21","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For me, to live is Christ "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 14:7–9","book":"Rom","chapter":14,"verse":7,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 2:19–20","book":"Gal","chapter":2,"verse":19,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 1:11","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":11,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 1:15","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":15,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 2:6","book":"Col","chapter":2,"verse":6,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" and to die is gain. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 8:38–39","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":38,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 3:7","book":"Php","chapter":3,"verse":7,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 14:7–9","book":"Rom","chapter":14,"verse":7},{"label":"Gl 2:19–20","book":"Gal","chapter":2,"verse":19},{"label":"Php 1:11","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":11},{"label":"Php 1:15","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":15},{"label":"Col 2:6","book":"Col","chapter":2,"verse":6},{"label":"Rm 8:38–39","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":38},{"label":"Php 3:7","book":"Php","chapter":3,"verse":7}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:22","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Now if I live on in the flesh, this means fruitful "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 3:8","book":"Mat","chapter":3,"verse":8,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 1:13","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":13,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 5:22","book":"Gal","chapter":5,"verse":22,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" work "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 14:6","book":"Mrk","chapter":14,"verse":6,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 3:10","book":"Gal","chapter":3,"verse":10,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jms 2:14","book":"Jas","chapter":2,"verse":14,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" for me; and I don’t know which one I should choose. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 3:8","book":"Mat","chapter":3,"verse":8},{"label":"Rm 1:13","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":13},{"label":"Gl 5:22","book":"Gal","chapter":5,"verse":22},{"label":"Mk 14:6","book":"Mrk","chapter":14,"verse":6},{"label":"Gl 3:10","book":"Gal","chapter":3,"verse":10},{"label":"Jms 2:14","book":"Jas","chapter":2,"verse":14}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:23","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I am torn between the two. I long to depart and be with Christ "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 6:8","book":"Rom","chapter":6,"verse":8,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 4:14","book":"2Co","chapter":4,"verse":14,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 13:4–5","book":"2Co","chapter":13,"verse":4,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Th 4:14","book":"1Th","chapter":4,"verse":14,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Th 5:9–10","book":"1Th","chapter":5,"verse":9,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" —which is far better "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 12:26","book":"Jhn","chapter":12,"verse":26,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" — "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 6:8","book":"Rom","chapter":6,"verse":8},{"label":"2Co 4:14","book":"2Co","chapter":4,"verse":14},{"label":"2Co 13:4–5","book":"2Co","chapter":13,"verse":4},{"label":"1Th 4:14","book":"1Th","chapter":4,"verse":14},{"label":"1Th 5:9–10","book":"1Th","chapter":5,"verse":9},{"label":"Jn 12:26","book":"Jhn","chapter":12,"verse":26}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:24","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"but to remain in the flesh is more necessary for your sake. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:25","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Since I am persuaded of this, I know that I will remain and continue with all of you for your progress and joy in the faith, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 8:10","book":"Mat","chapter":8,"verse":10,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 3:16","book":"Act","chapter":3,"verse":16,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 1:8","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":8,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 2:5","book":"1Co","chapter":2,"verse":5,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 2:16","book":"Gal","chapter":2,"verse":16,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Tm 1:2","book":"1Ti","chapter":1,"verse":2,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 4:2","book":"Heb","chapter":4,"verse":2,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jd 1:3","book":"Jud","chapter":1,"verse":3,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 8:10","book":"Mat","chapter":8,"verse":10},{"label":"Ac 3:16","book":"Act","chapter":3,"verse":16},{"label":"Rm 1:8","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":8},{"label":"1Co 2:5","book":"1Co","chapter":2,"verse":5},{"label":"Gl 2:16","book":"Gal","chapter":2,"verse":16},{"label":"1Tm 1:2","book":"1Ti","chapter":1,"verse":2},{"label":"Heb 4:2","book":"Heb","chapter":4,"verse":2},{"label":"Jd 1:3","book":"Jud","chapter":1,"verse":3}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:26","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"so that, because of my coming to you again, your boasting "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 15:58","book":"1Co","chapter":15,"verse":58,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" in Christ Jesus "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 16:7","book":"Rom","chapter":16,"verse":7,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 2:6","book":"Eph","chapter":2,"verse":6,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 5:14","book":"1Pe","chapter":5,"verse":14,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" may abound."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Co 15:58","book":"1Co","chapter":15,"verse":58},{"label":"Rm 16:7","book":"Rom","chapter":16,"verse":7},{"label":"Eph 2:6","book":"Eph","chapter":2,"verse":6},{"label":"1Pt 5:14","book":"1Pe","chapter":5,"verse":14}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:27","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Just one thing: As citizens of heaven, live your life "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 23:1","book":"Act","chapter":23,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" worthy of the gospel of Christ. Then, whether I come and see you or am absent, I will hear about you that you are standing firm "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 16:13","book":"1Co","chapter":16,"verse":13,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 5:1","book":"Gal","chapter":5,"verse":1,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 6:13–17","book":"Eph","chapter":6,"verse":13,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 4:1","book":"Php","chapter":4,"verse":1,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Th 2:15","book":"2Th","chapter":2,"verse":15,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" in one "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 11:52","book":"Jhn","chapter":11,"verse":52,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" spirit, in one accord, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit soul"},{"kind":"text","text":" contending together for the faith "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Tm 3:9","book":"1Ti","chapter":3,"verse":9,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Tm 4:1","book":"1Ti","chapter":4,"verse":1,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Tm 4:6","book":"1Ti","chapter":4,"verse":6,"letter":"j"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Tm 5:8","book":"1Ti","chapter":5,"verse":8,"letter":"k"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Tm 6:10","book":"1Ti","chapter":6,"verse":10,"letter":"l"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Tm 6:21","book":"1Ti","chapter":6,"verse":21,"letter":"m"},{"kind":"text","text":" of the gospel, "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 23:1","book":"Act","chapter":23,"verse":1},{"label":"1Co 16:13","book":"1Co","chapter":16,"verse":13},{"label":"Gl 5:1","book":"Gal","chapter":5,"verse":1},{"label":"Eph 6:13–17","book":"Eph","chapter":6,"verse":13},{"label":"Php 4:1","book":"Php","chapter":4,"verse":1},{"label":"2Th 2:15","book":"2Th","chapter":2,"verse":15},{"label":"Jn 11:52","book":"Jhn","chapter":11,"verse":52},{"label":"1Tm 3:9","book":"1Ti","chapter":3,"verse":9},{"label":"1Tm 4:1","book":"1Ti","chapter":4,"verse":1},{"label":"1Tm 4:6","book":"1Ti","chapter":4,"verse":6},{"label":"1Tm 5:8","book":"1Ti","chapter":5,"verse":8},{"label":"1Tm 6:10","book":"1Ti","chapter":6,"verse":10},{"label":"1Tm 6:21","book":"1Ti","chapter":6,"verse":21}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit soul"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:28","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"not being frightened in any way by your opponents. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 16:9","book":"1Co","chapter":16,"verse":9,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" This is a sign of destruction for them, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 7:13","book":"Mat","chapter":7,"verse":13,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 9:22","book":"Rom","chapter":9,"verse":22,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" but of your salvation "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 4:12","book":"Act","chapter":4,"verse":12,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 7:10","book":"2Co","chapter":7,"verse":10,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 5:9","book":"Heb","chapter":5,"verse":9,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" —and this is from God. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Co 16:9","book":"1Co","chapter":16,"verse":9},{"label":"Mt 7:13","book":"Mat","chapter":7,"verse":13},{"label":"Rm 9:22","book":"Rom","chapter":9,"verse":22},{"label":"Ac 4:12","book":"Act","chapter":4,"verse":12},{"label":"2Co 7:10","book":"2Co","chapter":7,"verse":10},{"label":"Heb 5:9","book":"Heb","chapter":5,"verse":9}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:29","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For it has been granted to you on Christ’s behalf not only to believe "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 11:24","book":"Mrk","chapter":11,"verse":24,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 3:16","book":"Jhn","chapter":3,"verse":16,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 10:43","book":"Act","chapter":10,"verse":43,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 10:9","book":"Rom","chapter":10,"verse":9,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 1:8","book":"1Pe","chapter":1,"verse":8,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" in him, but also to suffer for him, "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mk 11:24","book":"Mrk","chapter":11,"verse":24},{"label":"Jn 3:16","book":"Jhn","chapter":3,"verse":16},{"label":"Ac 10:43","book":"Act","chapter":10,"verse":43},{"label":"Rm 10:9","book":"Rom","chapter":10,"verse":9},{"label":"1Pt 1:8","book":"1Pe","chapter":1,"verse":8}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Php:1:30","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"since you are engaged in the same struggle that you saw I had and now hear that I have."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]}]},"cachedAt":1783099548133}